      "html": "\n<div class=\"brand-details-container bg-white text-[#1A0B2E] font-['Montserrat'] min-h-screen relative\" data-kid=\"0\">\n    <style data-kid=\"1\">\n        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=Montserrat:wght@200;300;400;500;600;700&display=swap');\n        @import url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tabler/icons-webfont/tabler-icons.min.css');\n\n        :root {\n            --color-bg: #FFFFFF;\n            --color-text: #1A0B2E;\n            --color-accent: #9D4EDD;\n            --color-border: #F3E8FF;\n            --color-surface: #FAFAFF;\n            --font-serif: 'Playfair Display', serif;\n            --font-sans: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;\n            --shadow-premium: 40px 40px 80px rgba(26, 11, 46, 0.08);\n        }\n\n        .font-serif { font-family: var(--font-serif); }\n        .font-sans { font-family: var(--font-sans); }\n        .tracking-ultra { letter-spacing: 0.5em; }\n\n        .vertical-text {\n            writing-mode: vertical-rl;\n            text-orientation: mixed;\n            transform: rotate(180deg);\n        }\n\n        .no-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }\n        .no-scrollbar { -ms-overflow-style: none; scrollbar-width: none; }\n\n        /* Global Grid Lines Overlay */\n        .grid-lines {\n            position: absolute;\n            inset: 0;\n            pointer-events: none;\n            display: flex;\n            z-index: 5;\n        }\n        .grid-line {\n            width: 25%;\n            height: 100%;\n            border-right: 1px solid var(--color-border);\n        }\n        .grid-line:last-child { border-right: none; }\n\n        /* Drop caps */\n        .drop-cap::first-letter {\n            font-family: var(--font-serif);\n            font-size: 5rem;\n            color: var(--color-accent);\n            float: left;\n            line-height: 0.8;\n            margin-right: 0.75rem;\n            margin-top: 0.5rem;\n        }\n    </style>\n\n    \n    <nav class=\"fixed top-0 left-0 w-full px-12 py-8 flex justify-between items-center bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-[#F3E8FF] z-[100]\" data-kid=\"2\">\n        <div class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.4em] uppercase font-bold opacity-60\" data-kid=\"3\">Vol. 03 / Brand Details</div>\n        <div class=\"text-xl font-serif tracking-[0.2em] font-bold\" data-kid=\"4\">REFULGENT LUXURY</div>\n        <div class=\"flex gap-8 text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase font-bold\" data-kid=\"5\">\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"opacity-60 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\" data-kid=\"6\">Archive</a>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"opacity-60 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\" data-kid=\"7\">Philosophy</a>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-[#9D4EDD]\" data-kid=\"8\">About</a>\n        </div>\n    </nav>\n\n    \n    <div class=\"relative pt-24\" data-kid=\"9\">\n        \n        \n        <section class=\"relative h-[900px] border-b border-[#F3E8FF] overflow-hidden\" data-kid=\"10\">\n            <div class=\"grid-lines\" data-kid=\"11\">\n                <div class=\"grid-line\" data-kid=\"12\"></div>\n                <div class=\"grid-line\" data-kid=\"13\"></div>\n                <div class=\"grid-line\" data-kid=\"14\"></div>\n                <div class=\"grid-line\" data-kid=\"15\"></div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"relative z-10 grid grid-cols-4 h-full\" data-kid=\"16\">\n                \n                <div class=\"flex flex-col justify-end p-12\" data-kid=\"17\">\n                    <div class=\"vertical-text text-[10px] tracking-[0.8em] font-bold opacity-20 uppercase mb-24\" data-kid=\"18\">\n                        SINCE MMXII • PARIS\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                \n                <div class=\"pt-48 px-12\" data-kid=\"19\">\n                    <span class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.5em] font-bold text-[#9D4EDD] mb-12 block uppercase\" data-kid=\"20\">01 / The Story</span>\n                    <h1 class=\"font-serif text-[110px] leading-[0.9] tracking-tighter text-[#1A0B2E]\" data-kid=\"21\">\n                        The<br data-kid=\"22\">Architecture<br data-kid=\"23\">of Beauty\n                    </h1>\n                </div>\n\n                \n                <div class=\"pt-64 px-12\" data-kid=\"24\">\n                    <div class=\"max-w-xs\" data-kid=\"25\">\n                        <p class=\"text-base font-light leading-[1.8] opacity-70 mb-10\" data-kid=\"26\">\n                            Refulgent Luxury was born from a singular obsession: the way light interacts with the human epidermis. We believe that skincare is an architectural undertaking—a precise layering of molecular science and botanical raw materials to build a foundation of lasting radiance.\n                        </p>\n                        <p class=\"text-base font-light leading-[1.8] opacity-70\" data-kid=\"27\">\n                            Our Parisian atelier serves as a laboratory for the soul, where blueprints for ethereal beauty are drafted, tested, and realized with the same structural integrity as a modern masterpiece.\n                        </p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                \n                <div class=\"relative h-full\" data-kid=\"28\">\n                    <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1757620057654-7d25721ac59f?auto=format&w=800&q=80&fit=crop\" alt=\"Architectural Vanity Shadow\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover grayscale-[0.2] hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-1000\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" data-kid=\"29\">\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        \n        <section class=\"py-40 relative\" data-kid=\"30\">\n            <div class=\"grid-lines\" data-kid=\"31\">\n                <div class=\"grid-line\" data-kid=\"32\"></div>\n                <div class=\"grid-line\" data-kid=\"33\"></div>\n                <div class=\"grid-line\" data-kid=\"34\"></div>\n                <div class=\"grid-line\" data-kid=\"35\"></div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"container mx-auto px-12 relative z-10\" data-kid=\"36\">\n                <div class=\"mb-24 flex justify-between items-end border-b border-[#F3E8FF] pb-12\" data-kid=\"37\">\n                    <div data-kid=\"38\">\n                        <span class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.5em] font-bold text-[#9D4EDD] mb-4 block uppercase\" data-kid=\"39\">02 / Foundations</span>\n                        <h2 class=\"font-serif text-6xl\" data-kid=\"40\">Core Principles</h2>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] font-bold opacity-30 uppercase max-w-[200px]\" data-kid=\"41\">\n                        Engineering a new standard in clinical ethereality.\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-0 border border-[#F3E8FF]\" data-kid=\"42\">\n                    \n                    <div class=\"bg-[#FAFAFF] border-r border-[#F3E8FF] p-24 aspect-square flex flex-col justify-between group\" data-kid=\"43\">\n                        <div class=\"flex justify-between items-start\" data-kid=\"44\">\n                            <span class=\"font-serif text-6xl text-[#9D4EDD] opacity-10 italic\" data-kid=\"45\">I.</span>\n                            <span class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.5em] font-bold opacity-40 uppercase group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\" data-kid=\"46\">The Vision</span>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"relative\" data-kid=\"47\">\n                            <p class=\"text-2xl font-light leading-[1.8] opacity-80 drop-cap\" data-kid=\"48\">\n                                To pioneer a new era of \"Clinical Ethereality\"—where the precision of molecular science and the luxury of high-end design coexist in perfect, radiant symmetry. We see a world where beauty is an architectural feat.\n                            </p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"h-[1px] w-32 bg-[#9D4EDD]/40 group-hover:w-full transition-all duration-700\" data-kid=\"49\"></div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    \n                    <div class=\"bg-[#FAFAFF] p-24 aspect-square flex flex-col justify-between group\" data-kid=\"50\">\n                        <div class=\"flex justify-between items-start\" data-kid=\"51\">\n                            <span class=\"font-serif text-6xl text-[#9D4EDD] opacity-10 italic\" data-kid=\"52\">II.</span>\n                            <span class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.5em] font-bold opacity-40 uppercase group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\" data-kid=\"53\">The Mission</span>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"relative\" data-kid=\"54\">\n                            <p class=\"text-2xl font-light leading-[1.8] opacity-80 drop-cap\" data-kid=\"55\">\n                                We are dedicated to crafting high-performance skincare that honors the integrity of the skin's barrier while elevating the daily ritual of self-care into an art form. Every drop is a commitment to sustainable excellence.\n                            </p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"h-[1px] w-32 bg-[#9D4EDD]/40 group-hover:w-full transition-all duration-700\" data-kid=\"56\"></div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        \n        <section class=\"py-40 bg-[#FAFAFF]/30 overflow-hidden relative border-y border-[#F3E8FF]\" data-kid=\"57\">\n             <div class=\"grid-lines\" data-kid=\"58\">\n                <div class=\"grid-line\" data-kid=\"59\"></div>\n                <div class=\"grid-line\" data-kid=\"60\"></div>\n                <div class=\"grid-line\" data-kid=\"61\"></div>\n                <div class=\"grid-line\" data-kid=\"62\"></div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"container mx-auto px-12 relative z-10\" data-kid=\"63\">\n                <div class=\"mb-32 flex items-center gap-12\" data-kid=\"64\">\n                    <h2 class=\"font-serif text-8xl leading-none\" data-kid=\"65\">The Creators</h2>\n                    <div class=\"h-[1px] flex-grow bg-[#F3E8FF]\" data-kid=\"66\"></div>\n                    <span class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.5em] font-bold text-[#9D4EDD] uppercase whitespace-nowrap\" data-kid=\"67\">03 / Leadership</span>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"flex gap-40 overflow-x-auto pb-12 no-scrollbar\" data-kid=\"68\">\n                    \n                    <div class=\"flex items-end flex-shrink-0 relative group\" data-kid=\"69\">\n                        <div class=\"vertical-text text-[11px] tracking-[1.5em] font-bold opacity-30 uppercase absolute -left-16 bottom-0 transition-opacity group-hover:opacity-100\" data-kid=\"70\">\n                            VANCE\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"w-[500px] aspect-[3/4] overflow-hidden grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-1000 shadow-premium\" data-kid=\"71\">\n                            <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1766297247924-6638d54e7c89?auto=format&w=1000&q=80&fit=crop\" alt=\"Dr. Elara Vance\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover transform group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-1000\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" data-kid=\"72\">\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"absolute -right-8 bottom-12 bg-white p-8 border border-[#F3E8FF] max-w-[200px] translate-x-12 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:translate-x-0 transition-all duration-500\" data-kid=\"73\">\n                            <span class=\"text-[9px] font-bold tracking-widest text-[#9D4EDD] uppercase mb-2 block\" data-kid=\"74\">Chief Science Officer</span>\n                            <p class=\"text-[11px] font-light leading-relaxed opacity-60\" data-kid=\"75\">Molecular biology expert with 15 years in Parisian labs.</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    \n                    <div class=\"flex items-end flex-shrink-0 relative group\" data-kid=\"76\">\n                        <div class=\"vertical-text text-[11px] tracking-[1.5em] font-bold opacity-30 uppercase absolute -left-16 bottom-0 transition-opacity group-hover:opacity-100\" data-kid=\"77\">\n                            MARCEL\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"w-[500px] aspect-[3/4] overflow-hidden grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-1000 shadow-premium\" data-kid=\"78\">\n                            <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1766297247913-54717c00e79c?auto=format&w=1000&q=80&fit=crop\" alt=\"Julian Marcel\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover transform group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-1000\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" data-kid=\"79\">\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"absolute -right-8 bottom-12 bg-white p-8 border border-[#F3E8FF] max-w-[200px] translate-x-12 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:translate-x-0 transition-all duration-500\" data-kid=\"80\">\n                            <span class=\"text-[9px] font-bold tracking-widest text-[#9D4EDD] uppercase mb-2 block\" data-kid=\"81\">Creative Director</span>\n                            <p class=\"text-[11px] font-light leading-relaxed opacity-60\" data-kid=\"82\">Visionary in luxury brand architecture and aesthetic purity.</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        \n        <section class=\"py-56 relative bg-white\" data-kid=\"83\">\n            <div class=\"grid-lines\" data-kid=\"84\">\n                <div class=\"grid-line\" data-kid=\"85\"></div>\n                <div class=\"grid-line\" data-kid=\"86\"></div>\n                <div class=\"grid-line\" data-kid=\"87\"></div>\n                <div class=\"grid-line\" data-kid=\"88\"></div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"container mx-auto px-12 relative z-10\" data-kid=\"89\">\n                <div class=\"relative max-w-6xl mx-auto group\" data-kid=\"90\">\n                    \n                    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-[#1A0B2E] translate-x-8 translate-y-8 rounded-sm shadow-2xl transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:translate-x-10 group-hover:translate-y-10\" data-kid=\"91\"></div>\n                    \n                    \n                    <div class=\"relative bg-white border border-[#F3E8FF] p-24 flex items-center gap-16 overflow-hidden\" data-kid=\"92\">\n                        \n                        <div class=\"w-1/2 flex items-center justify-center relative\" data-kid=\"93\">\n                            <div class=\"font-serif italic text-[260px] leading-none text-[#1A0B2E] font-light select-none tracking-tighter\" data-kid=\"94\">\n                                100<span class=\"text-8xl align-top -ml-4\" data-kid=\"95\">%</span>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-80 h-80 bg-[#9D4EDD]/5 rounded-full blur-[100px] -z-10\" data-kid=\"96\"></div>\n                        </div>\n\n                        \n                        <div class=\"w-1/2\" data-kid=\"97\">\n                            <div class=\"mb-10\" data-kid=\"98\">\n                                <span class=\"text-[11px] tracking-[0.5em] font-bold text-[#9D4EDD] uppercase mb-6 block\" data-kid=\"99\">04 / Sustainability</span>\n                                <h3 class=\"font-serif text-6xl mb-8 leading-[1.1]\" data-kid=\"100\">Sustainable<br data-kid=\"101\">by Architecture</h3>\n                                <p class=\"text-xl font-light leading-relaxed opacity-70 mb-12\" data-kid=\"102\">\n                                    Our commitment to 100% recyclable packaging is not just a policy—it's a design requirement. From pharmaceutical-grade glass to biodegradable sealants, every element is engineered for a circular lifespan.\n                                </p>\n                                <div class=\"flex items-center gap-6\" data-kid=\"103\">\n                                    <div class=\"w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-[#FAFAFF] flex items-center justify-center border border-[#F3E8FF]\" data-kid=\"104\">\n                                        <i class=\"ti ti-leaf text-2xl text-[#9D4EDD]\" data-kid=\"105\"></i>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"text-[11px] tracking-widest font-bold uppercase cursor-pointer hover:text-[#9D4EDD] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"106\">\n                                        View our 2024 Ethics Blueprint\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n\n                        \n                        <div class=\"absolute right-0 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 vertical-text text-[9px] tracking-[2em] font-bold opacity-10 uppercase\" data-kid=\"107\">\n                            ETHEREAL • RESPONSIBLE • TIMELESS\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        \n        <footer class=\"bg-[#FAFAFF] py-32 border-t border-[#F3E8FF] relative overflow-hidden\" data-kid=\"108\">\n             <div class=\"grid-lines opacity-30\" data-kid=\"109\">\n                <div class=\"grid-line\" data-kid=\"110\"></div>\n                <div class=\"grid-line\" data-kid=\"111\"></div>\n                <div class=\"grid-line\" data-kid=\"112\"></div>\n                <div class=\"grid-line\" data-kid=\"113\"></div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"container mx-auto px-12 relative z-10\" data-kid=\"114\">\n                <div class=\"grid grid-cols-4 gap-20\" data-kid=\"115\">\n                    <div class=\"col-span-1\" data-kid=\"116\">\n                        <div class=\"text-2xl font-serif font-bold mb-10\" data-kid=\"117\">Refulgent Luxury</div>\n                        <p class=\"text-sm font-light leading-relaxed opacity-60 mb-10\" data-kid=\"118\">\n                            A museum of skincare, curated for the modern minimalist who demands both aesthetic purity and clinical performance.\n                        </p>\n                        <div class=\"flex gap-6\" data-kid=\"119\">\n                            <a href=\"#\" class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-[#F3E8FF] flex items-center justify-center opacity-60 hover:opacity-100 hover:border-[#9D4EDD] hover:text-[#9D4EDD] transition-all\" data-kid=\"120\"><i class=\"ti ti-brand-instagram\" data-kid=\"121\"></i></a>\n                            <a href=\"#\" class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-[#F3E8FF] flex items-center justify-center opacity-60 hover:opacity-100 hover:border-[#9D4EDD] hover:text-[#9D4EDD] transition-all\" data-kid=\"122\"><i class=\"ti ti-brand-pinterest\" data-kid=\"123\"></i></a>\n                            <a href=\"#\" class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-[#F3E8FF] flex items-center justify-center opacity-60 hover:opacity-100 hover:border-[#9D4EDD] hover:text-[#9D4EDD] transition-all\" data-kid=\"124\"><i class=\"ti ti-brand-youtube\" data-kid=\"125\"></i></a>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div class=\"col-span-1 pt-4\" data-kid=\"126\">\n                        <h5 class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.4em] uppercase font-bold opacity-30 mb-8\" data-kid=\"127\">Navigation</h5>\n                        <ul class=\"flex flex-col gap-4 text-xs font-semibold\" data-kid=\"128\">\n                            <li data-kid=\"129\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#9D4EDD] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"130\">Archive</a></li>\n                            <li data-kid=\"131\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#9D4EDD] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"132\">Laboratory</a></li>\n                            <li data-kid=\"133\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#9D4EDD] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"134\">Sustainability</a></li>\n                            <li data-kid=\"135\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#9D4EDD] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"136\">Shop All</a></li>\n                        </ul>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div class=\"col-span-1 pt-4\" data-kid=\"137\">\n                        <h5 class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.4em] uppercase font-bold opacity-30 mb-8\" data-kid=\"138\">Legal</h5>\n                        <ul class=\"flex flex-col gap-4 text-xs font-semibold\" data-kid=\"139\">\n                            <li data-kid=\"140\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#9D4EDD] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"141\">Privacy Blueprint</a></li>\n                            <li data-kid=\"142\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#9D4EDD] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"143\">Terms of Use</a></li>\n                            <li data-kid=\"144\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#9D4EDD] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"145\">Accessibility</a></li>\n                            <li data-kid=\"146\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#9D4EDD] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"147\">Shipping Ethics</a></li>\n                        </ul>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div class=\"col-span-1 pt-4\" data-kid=\"148\">\n                        <h5 class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.4em] uppercase font-bold opacity-30 mb-8\" data-kid=\"149\">Journal</h5>\n                        <p class=\"text-xs opacity-60 mb-6\" data-kid=\"150\">Receive our seasonal editorial on beauty and architecture.</p>\n                        <div class=\"relative\" data-kid=\"151\">\n                            <input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"Email Address\" class=\"w-full bg-transparent border-b border-[#1A0B2E]/20 py-3 text-xs outline-none focus:border-[#9D4EDD] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"152\">\n                            <button class=\"absolute right-0 bottom-3 text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase font-bold text-[#9D4EDD]\" data-kid=\"153\">Subscribe</button>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"mt-32 pt-10 border-t border-[#F3E8FF] flex justify-between items-center\" data-kid=\"154\">\n                    <div class=\"text-[9px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase font-bold opacity-40\" data-kid=\"155\">© 2024 REFULGENT LUXURY ATELIER</div>\n                    <div class=\"text-[9px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase font-bold opacity-40\" data-kid=\"156\">DESIGNED BY MUSEUM COLLECTIVE</div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        \n    </footer>\n</div>\n</div>",
